    <label>Glock 17L</label>
    <description>"The Glock 17L is a long-barreled variant of the popular Glock 17 pistol. Renowned for its accuracy and reliability, this semi-automatic handgun excels in medium-range engagements. Its extended barrel offers improved ballistic performance, making it a favored choice for marksmen requiring superior precision in a compact package. Though it lacks the stopping power of larger firearms, its rapid rate of fire and manageable recoil make it a versatile sidearm in any colony's arsenal."</description>
